citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:00pm-7:00pm on
8/19/2025. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee/registrant by ringing the doorbell. The inspector also called
and left a message. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a serious violation of
the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
